{
  "stem": "5371.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they made me do a lot of things, you know, where I jeopardized my life, but naturally, they didn't care about it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- We-- there's so many things, you know, that happened that it's impossible to remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Where you, you get like a mental block at certain times, where you try to remember.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then after a while, when you get together with people who you were there, you, you remember after you talk, and you get reminded of certain incidents.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then you, you bring in, you come in with a lot of things that you remember.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But in general, it's very, very hard to remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When we were moved from Auschwitz to Birkenau, I worked in the gypsy camp many days, on and off.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was so beautiful there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Even they were incarcerated, but they were with their families, with their children, with their babies.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had babies in there too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we-- I used to talk to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I, I, I enjoyed being there, because, you know, I missed so much of my own family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[CRYING] But after a while, naturally, they were all put into the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was only a matter of days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Everyone knew there was only a matter of days till our own time will come.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Many days you walked out into the camp, and the fences were all electrified.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And you saw people hanging on the, on the, on the fence who committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember cases when I came first to Birkenau, and they had only one crematorium.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what they did in the beginning, is after they gassed the people, they threw them into ditches, and they were burning the people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some people were alive, you know it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember one--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
